dc_description_s: This data represents addresses for Dane County, Wisconsin in 2023.[This feature layer consists of address points for buildings, units and parcels that have been assigned an address by the local addressing authority in Dane County, Wisconsin. Currently, address points for the City of Madison and City of Sun Prairie are not included, but will eventually be part of future publishes of this feature layer.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://gis-countyofdane.opendata.arcgis.com/
